WEBVTT

00:04:58.377 --> 00:05:00.563
and only 20 million students enrolled.

00:05:00.587 --> 00:05:02.007
Church can't do it, either --

00:05:02.031 --> 00:05:04.798
only 35 percent of us go
on a regular basis,

00:05:04.822 --> 00:05:06.185
and when we do,

00:05:06.209 --> 00:05:10.385
eleven o'clock Sunday morning
is "the most segregated hour" in America.

00:05:11.232 --> 00:05:12.632
But business?

00:05:12.656 --> 00:05:19.008
There are a 162 million people
in the US workforce alone --

00:05:19.032 --> 00:05:20.571
people of all races,

00:05:20.595 --> 00:05:25.087
united in the spirit of wanting a paycheck
and having to show up to get it.

00:05:25.111 --> 00:05:26.662
(Laughter)

00:05:27.458 --> 00:05:31.467
Now, I'm aware that diversity
is bigger than race,